cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with generating features for image classification tasks.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel method for improving the performance of zero-shot learning using transfer feature generating networks.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of machine learning models for image classification tasks.
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with semantic relationships between classes in image classification tasks.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with generating features for multimedia data (images).
